{{!--
/**
 * Loading Spinner Component Template
 *
 * PURPOSE:
 * Reusable component for displaying loading indicators during asynchronous operations.
 * Provides visual feedback with animated spinner and customizable size, along with
 * optional loading message text. Ensures consistent loading state presentation
 * across the application with proper accessibility support.
 *
 * CONTEXT REQUIREMENTS:
 * @param {number} [size] - Optional spinner size multiplier (defaults to 3x)
 * @param {string} [message] - Optional custom loading message (falls back to default)
 *
 * HELPER DEPENDENCIES:
 * @requires localize - Foundry VTT localization helper for text translation
 * @requires if - Handlebars conditional helper for parameter checking
 *
 * ACCESSIBILITY FEATURES:
 * - Status role for screen reader announcement of loading state
 * - Descriptive aria-label for loading context
 * - Spinner icon marked as decorative to avoid redundant announcement
 * - Semantic paragraph structure for loading message
 *
 * CUSTOMIZATION POINTS:
 * - Spinner size configurable through size parameter (1x, 2x, 3x, etc.)
 * - Loading message adaptable through context parameter
 * - Default size of 3x provides good visibility
 * - Default message ensures consistent user feedback
 *
 * INTEGRATION:
 * - Used across multiple templates for consistent loading display
 * - Supports async data loading, spell processing, and application initialization
 * - Integrates with application state management systems
 * - Provides user feedback during data operations
 */
--}}

<div class="loading-spinner" role="status" aria-label="{{localize 'SPELLBOOK.UI.Loading'}}">
	<i class="fas fa-spinner fa-spin fa-{{#if size}}{{size}}{{else}}3{{/if}}x" aria-hidden="true"></i>
	<p>{{#if message}}{{message}}{{else}}{{localize 'SPELLBOOK.UI.Loading'}}{{/if}}</p>
</div>
